reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice quality bed for the price!
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble. Bought this for my teenage son who’s 6’ and 150#. It’s held up well and looks surprisingly nice! The frame seems solid. The only issue is there is a leg in the middle on the side that seems to be perfectly located to hit your toes EVERY SINGLE TIME you go to get in bed. We just sliced a pool noodle and used black duct tape so you couldn’t tell. Problem solved. No more bonked toes.
